$lang['When converting hexadecimal to decimal, the first step is to divide the hex number by 16. This will give you the base number. The second step is to divide each digit of the hex number by 16 and write down the results. Finally, add up all of the numbers that were just calculated.'] = 'We yu de kɔnvɔyt heksadesimal to dɛsimal, di fɔs tin we yu fɔ du na fɔ sheb di heks nɔmba bay 16. Dis go gi yu di bays nɔmba. Di sɛkɔn tin we yu fɔ du na fɔ sheb ɛni dijit na di heks nɔmba bay 16 ɛn rayt di rizɔlt dɛn. Fɔ dɔn, ad ɔl di nɔmba dɛn we dɛn jɔs kɔl.';
